creator: Instructables Guides
title: Best of 2009: Most Commented
description: This text is an introduction to a series of guides showcasing the 'Best of 2009' Instructables, categorized by different metrics such as most comments, top-rated, and most viewed. It highlights a diverse range of projects published that year and notes that the instructables generated a lot of discussion and interest.
steps: Browse the list of Instructables that received the most comments in 2009.
Explore projects like the Z35 K'nex Assault Rifle, Gummi Bear Surgery, and Genuine Chainmaille From Pop Tabs.
Discover projects in various categories such as LEGO & K'NEX, Candy, Costumes & Cosplay, Apple, and Electronics.
Consider projects like the Mosin Nagant - M1891/1930 made from Knex, or a Solar IPod/iPhone Charger.
Look into projects like the K'nex AST Rifle, VSS Vintorez, Wireless Power, or AR-4 V3
